headline: How Investors May Respond To TE Connectivity (TEL) Doubling AI Sales Goal And Adding Dividend
summary: In late 2025, TE Connectivity held an Investor Day where it outlined plans to double AI-related sales within two years and confirmed its role supplying critical components to the AI hardware ecosystem, while its board also approved a new quarterly cash dividend as part of its capital return framework.
